text: This event is triggered by a system import with the Hold Execution setting enabled. The following fields are included: Name - The name of the workflow group that is mentioned in the eventMessage . Message - A textual description of the events that take place while systemimport -holdexecution is executing. Fields inherited from the Base event The following fields are inherited from the Base event, and described in more detail in Base Event : category contents eventName origin receiveTimeStamp severity timeStamp
